# myprintx ğŸ¨
A lightweight Python library that enhances the built-in `print()` function.

## Features
- âœ… Colorful output â€” control both foreground & background colors
- âœ… Text styles â€” support bold, italic, and underline
- âœ… Non-intrusive design â€” 100% compatible with the built-in print()
- âœ… Global patch â€” one-line activation for all print() calls
- âœ… Auto prefix â€” show date, time, tag, and location info
- âœ… Built-in log helpers â€” info(), warn(), error(), debug()

